    "Lack of historical data and the necessity of huge sets of data for model training could be another limitation.",
    "Moreover, many breeders could be reluctant to use AI for a trait of interest due to socio-economic or personal preferences.",
    "Also, AI algorithms could not be suitable for all or generalized for all scenarios.",
    "The use of virtual assistance or chat bots to answer the simple questions of farmers is also on the rise.",
    "The AI powered chat bots use natural language conversation algorithms to provide more personalized conversation."
